  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-burger-bowl-with-pickled-onions/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, crumble your <strong>meat-free patty[ies] </strong>into the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-burger-bowl-with-pickled-onions/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add <strong>3/4 </strong>of the <strong>sliced onion</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 5-6 min or until the burgers are cooked through and lightly charred</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-burger-bowl-with-pickled-onions/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) with a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and a splash of <strong>boiled water</strong> to a small bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>onions</strong> to the bowl and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-burger-bowl-with-pickled-onions/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> roughly</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-burger-bowl-with-pickled-onions/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mustard ketchup</strong>,<strong> mayo </strong>and the <strong>remaining vinegar </strong>in a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>burger sauce salad dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-burger-bowl-with-pickled-onions/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>chopped tomato[es] </strong>to the bowl<strong> </strong>and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/plant-based-burger-bowl-with-pickled-onions/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong>, discard the liquid</p><p>Serve the <strong>dressed salad</strong> at the bottom of a bowl, top with the<strong> cooked</strong> <strong>meat-free burger </strong>and the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Dollop your <strong>sweet pepper relish </strong>over the top and garnish with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>and <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
